'''水野索諾亞'''（{{Nihongo|'''Sonoya Mizuno'''|ソノヤ・ミズノ}}，風格化作'''SONOYA'''<ref name="Mail 2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2161039/Future-stars-given-step-revolutionary-new-ballet-company.html|title=Ballet's got talent|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Daily Mail|last1=Slater|first1=Lidya|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081849/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2161039/Future-stars-given-step-revolutionary-new-ballet-company.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{bd|1986年|7月1日|catIdx=Mizuno, Sonoya}}），是一位[[日本|日本裔]][[英国|英國籍]]的[[演員|演員]]、[[模特兒|模特兒]]及[[芭蕾舞者|芭蕾舞者]]。

== 生平與職涯 ==
水野出生於[[東京|東京]]，並成長於[[英格兰|英格蘭]]的[[森麻實郡|森麻實郡]]。<ref name="Herald">{{Cite web|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/business/film/15-for-2015-sonoya-mizuno.115151930|title=15 for 2015: Sonoya Mizuno|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Herald Scotland|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523110717/http://www.heraldscotland.com/business/film/15-for-2015-sonoya-mizuno.115151930|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的父親是一位來自日本的藝術指導，她母親的雙親是分別來自英國與阿根廷的外交官；她的父母在日本相遇於1970年代。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/sonoya-mizuno|title=Sonoya MIZUNO|newspaper=Interview Magazine|accessdate=2016-12-26|archive-date=2016-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226151515/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/sonoya-mizuno|dead-url=no}}</ref>她自幼即進入[[皇家芭蕾舞學院|皇家芭蕾舞學院]]就讀<ref name="Mail 2012"/>，畢業後於數個芭蕾舞團工作，例如位在[[德累斯顿|德累斯顿]]的''Semperoper Ballet、''<ref name="HDS">{{Cite web|url=http://www.highstrungdancemovie.com/flv_portfolio/sonoya-mizuno-jazzy/|title=Sonoya Mizuno|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=High Strung Dance Movie|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205120922/http://www.highstrungdancemovie.com/flv_portfolio/sonoya-mizuno-jazzy/|archivedate=2015年2月5日}}</ref> ''Ballet Ireland、New English Ballet Theatre'' 以及''Scottish Ballet''。<ref name="Mail 2012"/><ref name="Herald"/> 因為芭蕾職涯所帶來的種種挫折，她在20歲時開始模特兒生涯，<ref name="Mail 2012"/> 並為[[香奈儿|香奈兒、]]亞歷山大·麥昆 、[[伊夫圣洛朗|聖羅蘭]]以及[[路易威登|路易威登]]擔任模特兒。<ref name="Herald"/> 2014年，水野現身於Arthur Pita的舞蹈劇''The World's Greatest Show'' ，該劇演出於''Greenwich Dance''以及[[皇家歌劇院|皇家歌劇院]]。<ref name="HDS"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.roh.org.uk/news/ladies-and-gentlemen-how-long-can-they-last-the-disturbing-1930s-craze-of-dance-marathons-|title=‘Ladies and gentlemen, how long can they last?’: The disturbing 1930s craze of dance marathons|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Royal Opera House|last1=Thomas|first1=Rachel}}</ref>

水野的電影出道作品是由[[亚力克斯·嘉兰|亚力克斯·嘉兰]]執導的 [[科學幻想|科幻]][[驚悚|驚悚片]]《[[机械姬|机械姬]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ex_machina/|title=Ex Machina|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205122119/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ex_machina/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；不過，她在該片中的角色設定引發了一些議論。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://multiasianfamilies.blogspot.tw/2015/05/how-ex-machina-abuses-women-of-color.html|title=How 'Ex Machina' Abuses Women of Color & Nobody Cares Cause It's Smart|accessdate=2016-12-27|work=multiasianfamilies.blogspot.tw|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227075650/http://multiasianfamilies.blogspot.tw/2015/05/how-ex-machina-abuses-women-of-color.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://rosemaryspixie.com/2015/04/26/ex-machina-and-the-puppetry-of-the-patriarch/|title=Ex Machina and the Puppetry of the Patriarch|accessdate=2016-12-27|date=2015-04-26|work=rosemary's pixie|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227080048/https://rosemaryspixie.com/2015/04/26/ex-machina-and-the-puppetry-of-the-patriarch/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Herald"/> 她也出現在舞蹈片《[[舞力重擊|舞力重擊]]》，該片由邁克爾·達米安執導並上映於2016年。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://movie.yam.com/article/166569|title=電影特區-俄羅斯舞團首位美裔舞者琪南坎帕 大銀幕處女作  《舞力重擊》高難度舞步全親自上陣 《人造意識》水野索諾亞 競飆舞技大秀姣好身段|accessdate=2016-12-27|work=電影特區|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227075111/http://movie.yam.com/article/166569|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201607040118-1.aspx|title=舞力重擊高難度舞步 主演親自上陣|last=中央通訊社|first=|date=|work=|accessdate=2016-12-27|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227074708/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201607040118-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HDS"/>她也在[[化學兄弟|化學兄弟]]和[[貝克_(歌手)|貝克]]發表於2016年的《Wide Open》音樂錄影帶中擔任特色舞者。<ref>{{Citation|last=ChemicalBrothersVEVO|title=The Chemical Brothers - Wide Open ft. Beck|date=2016-01-25|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BC2dRkm8ATU|accessdate=2016-12-26|archive-date=2016-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225124058/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BC2dRkm8ATU|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年8月，她現身於[[弗兰克·奥申|弗兰克·奥申]]的歌曲《Nikes》的音樂錄影帶之中。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vimeo.com/179791907|title=Frank Ocean - 'Nikes'|accessdate=2016-12-27|work=Vimeo|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227073607/https://vimeo.com/179791907|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.weareresonate.com/2016/10/interview-sonoya-mizuno-i-dont-fit-easily-casting-moulds-i-considered-different/|title=INTERVIEW: Sonoya Mizuno - "I don’t fit easily into casting moulds because I am considered different" - Resonate|date=2016-10-18|newspaper=Resonate|accessdate=2016-12-27|language=en-GB|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227072103/http://www.weareresonate.com/2016/10/interview-sonoya-mizuno-i-dont-fit-easily-casting-moulds-i-considered-different/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/news/a23630/la-la-land-actress-sonoya-mizuno/|title='La La Land' Actress Sonoya Mizuno Is, Like You, Obsessed with Food|date=2016-11-15|newspaper=Marie Claire|accessdate=2016-12-27|archive-date=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227074419/http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/news/a23630/la-la-land-actress-sonoya-mizuno/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

